<test>  ::= dist | codename | arch
<names> ::= ({ \w+ })
<expr>  ::= [ not ] <test> <names>
<if>    ::= @if <expr>
<elif>  ::= @elif <expr>
<else>  ::= @else
<endif> ::= @endif
<stmt>  ::= <if>
  [ text ]
[ ({ <elif> })
    [ text ]
]
[ <else>
    [ text ]
]
<endif>


example:

@if dist ubuntu debian
Build-Depends: ...
@elif dist maya
Build-Depends: ...
@else
@if not arch i386
Build-Depends: ...
@else
Build-Depends: ...
@end
